 out of China, was fined $550,000 in December in relation to the same case.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.tampabay.com/florida-politics/2019/03/12/jeb-bush-super-pac-fined-for-taking-13-million-in-illegal-money/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tampabay.com%2Fflorida-politics%2F2019%2F03%2F12%2Fjeb-bush-super-pac-fined-for-taking-13-million-in-illegal-money%2F&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=9ad2f32b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.tampabay.com/florida-politics/2019/03/12/jeb-bush-super-pac-fined-for-taking-13-million-in-illegal-money/</a>"}}